    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="546" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Persian.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: Oblong painting followed by two lines in two columns.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in nastaʻlīq in black ink; pointed.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Painting and reverse mostly in shades of orange, red and beige; frame in red with blue corners with pink vine designs; same design along long edge of frame.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Origin: Item is undated, probably produced in the late 19th or 20th century.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
